<template>
   <v-row justify="center">
    <v-col
      cols="12"
      sm="10"
      md="8"
      lg="6"
    >

    <v-divider class="mt-12">sfd</v-divider>

    <v-btn
      block
      elevation="2"
      x-large
      @click="abreImovel"
    >Imóveis</v-btn>

    <v-divider class="mt-6">sfd</v-divider>

    <v-btn
      block
      elevation="2"
      x-large
      @click="abreObjeto"
    >Objetos</v-btn>

    <v-divider class="mt-16">sfd</v-divider>
    <v-divider class="mt-16">sfd</v-divider>
    <v-divider class="mt-16">sfd</v-divider>


    <v-btn
      block
      elevation="2"
      x-large
      @click="abreUsuario"
    >Usuários</v-btn>
    <v-divider class="mt-6">sfd</v-divider>

    <v-btn
      block
      elevation="2"
      x-large
    >Sair</v-btn>

    </v-col>
  </v-row>
</template>


<script>

  import Imovel from  '@/services/imoveis'

  export default {

    imoveis: [],
    Selected: null,

    data () {
      return {
        imoveis: [],
        Selected: null,
      }     
    },

    mounted(){
      Imovel.getAll().then(resposta => {
        console.log(resposta.data)
        this.imoveis = resposta.data
      })
    },

    methods:{
      cadastroImovel(item){
        if (item != null)
          this.$router.push({name: 'imovelCadastro', params: {id: item}}); 
      }
    }

  }
</script>
